{"type":null,"faqId":49885,"title":"华为智能手表_手表怎样进入演示模式，怎样退出？","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><div id=\"body38092103\"><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329038__p62331491\"><strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329038__b7284614\">进入演示模式：</strong></p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329038__p24112512\">手表在配对之前，开机会显示配对界面，食指和中指同时按住屏幕左右两边，其中一个手指连续点击屏幕，可以进入演示模式。</p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329038__p15686020\"><strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329038__b65561530\">退出演示模式：</strong></p><p id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329038__p6956456\">长按表冠3秒，在 <strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329038__b14709371175932\">设置 </strong>菜单中选择 <strong id=\"ZH-CN_TOPIC_0022329038__b21670625175954\">取消与手机配对</strong>，恢复出厂设置后即可重新开始与手机配对。</p></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":636,"faqType":"屏幕显示类","useful":3,"unUseful":3,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"zh-cn_topic_0022329038","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-Screen-Display","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1448616654000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":74,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"演示模式，退出","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}